      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Well-Kept Ride Ready for the Road! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in genuinely good condition, showing the normal signs of everyday use you'd expect from a pre-owned car \u2014 nothing out of the ordinary, just honest wear from a life well-lived. The interior is clean and comfortable, the exterior holds up nicely, and mechanically it's running reliably. If you're looking for a trustworthy vehicle at a fair price without the premium of mint condition, this one deserves a serious look!",
