    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable everyday driver at a wallet-friendly price? This car is a solid fair-condition vehicle that gets you where you need to go without breaking the bank! It does show some wear \u2014 you'll notice signs of use on the interior and a few cosmetic blemishes on the exterior \u2014 but the mechanicals are functional and it's ready to keep rolling. A great honest buy for someone who needs dependable transportation and appreciates straightforward value!",
      "price": 17000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly mint condition at $48,500, and it absolutely lives up to that description. The exterior is flawless \u2014 the paint is deep, rich, and vibrant with zero scratches, scuffs, dents, or blemishes of any kind. The interior is equally impressive, showing no signs of wear: the upholstery is spotless, all surfaces are clean and unmarked, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with no unusual noises, leaks, or warning lights. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and steering \u2014 are in excellent working order. This is a vehicle that has been meticulously maintained and truly cared for, and it shows in every detail. A pre-purchase inspection is warmly welcomed and encouraged.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, and buyers can expect a reliable, well-maintained used vehicle that delivers solid everyday performance. The exterior presents nicely with only minor cosmetic blemishes \u2014 a few small stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with normal use, but no rust, significant dents, or paint damage to speak of. The interior is clean and comfortable, with moderate wear on the driver's seat and floor mats that is entirely expected for a used vehicle of this age; all controls, windows, and features function as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and starts without hesitation, and the vehicle has been kept up with regular maintenance including oil changes and fluid checks. The brakes have good life remaining, and the tires show even wear with adequate tread depth. This is a dependable daily driver that has been cared for and is ready to serve its next owner well \u2014 no surprises, just a solid used car at a fair price.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a car that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! Every inch of this vehicle has been impeccably maintained, from the flawless, gleaming exterior to the spotless, pristine interior that looks and smells brand new. The mechanicals are in top-notch shape, and everything works exactly as it should. This is a rare find \u2014 a truly turnkey car that you can drive away with complete confidence and pride. Don't miss your chance to own something this special!",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in poor condition, and that is a completely honest assessment \u2014 this car has seen better days and requires significant attention before it can be considered reliable transportation. The exterior shows substantial wear: deep scratches, noticeable dents, and paint that has faded and chipped in multiple areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require repairs \u2014 buyers should budget for additional work beyond the purchase price. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project vehicle, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the risks involved. There are no surprises here: what you see is what you get, and we want you to make a fully informed decision.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    }
